SCTX:
Begin ratScript

short ratskilled
short doonce

if ( doonce == -1 )
	return
endif

If ( OnDeath == 1 )
	set ratskilled to ratskilled + 1
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex EB_Pest >=25 )
	if ( GetJournalIndex EB_Pest <= 30 )
		if ( GetJournalIndex EB_Pest != 26 )
			if ( ratskilled == 10 )
				Journal "EB_Pest" 10
				set doonce to -1
			endif
		endif
	endif
endif


End ratScript
